<div style="z-index: 3;"><span class="titlebox" style="color: white;">Log Findings No. 1</span>
<br>
<br>
<center>[[File:Deadly old hag.webp|500x500px]]</center>
<br>
<center><span style="font-size: 40px; font-family: 'Protest Revolution';">'''"June 26, 2012"'''</span></center>
----
----
<br><br>
<div style="text-align:left;">
<div style="margin: 1em;">
<span style="font-family: 'Protest Revolution';">This creature... it seemed like something out of a fairy tale, not so whimsical. Baba Yaga, the witch from those old stories people told. As a child, I always believed it was real. But now, I wish I hadn't. Knowing that this thing exists... this beast... it shows no mercy.

<span style="font-family: 'Protest Revolution';">This forest, it was magical, it was, nice. Nice to be in peace. Though, no animals were there. Well, there were dead deer. Ignoring that, it was so peaceful, until I felt like I got hit with something. I passed out, though, I was only awake for seconds, and all I saw, was a void.

<span style="font-family: 'Protest Revolution';">Now, here I am. The place has never been as barren as before. It's so sad... But, what really lurks here is fucking disgusting...

<span style="font-family: 'Protest Revolution';">To anyone whoever finds this... '''<span style="color: red;">DONT ENTER THE CABIN.</span>'''
</div></div></div></div></div></div>

